  [Text] Burkina Faso's delegation to the swearing-in 
ceremony of the new South African president, led by the Assembly 
of People's Deputies' speaker Arsene Bongnessan Ye, was granted 
audience today by His Excellency Nelson Mandela. Other members 
of the delegation are External Relations Minister Ablasseh 
Ouedraogo and Salif Diallo, minister of special duties at the 
Presidency of Burkina Faso. 
