  [Text] In the second phase of his visit to African 
countries, our foreign minister met the president and other 
officials of Burkina Faso yesterday. The Burkina Faso president 
described their talks as positive and called for increased 
political contacts and agricultural and development cooperation 
as well as for exhibitions of Iranian products in his country. 
