<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Commentary on `New Look' Toward Africa </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC3103082394 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 0345 GMT 31 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC3103082394 </F>
