<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    National Session on Economy Ends; Proposals Issued </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AB1205182694 Ouagadougou Radiodiffusion Nationale du Burkina 
Radio in French 1300 GMT 11 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> AB1205182694 </F>
